22 transfers to:
23 (a) The Nebraska State Patrol Cash Fund: $115,000 less the
24 unexpended balance existing on June 30, 2025, in (i) the Nebraska State
25 Patrol Cash Fund, (ii) the Investigation Petty Cash Fund, (iii) any
26 special checking account or accounts used by the Nebraska State Patrol,
27 and (iv) the possession of agency personnel involved in investigations,
28 when the unexpended balances resulted from General Fund transfers to the
29 Nebraska State Patrol Cash Fund or from General Fund appropriations. Any
30 transfers made shall be subject to a final reconciliation of available
31 investigation cash fund balances as of June 30, 2025, by the Nebraska
